<strong>Objective of the programme</strong><br />
In present time, some big Institution run their certificate/ diploma programme in higher charges, due to which the lower and middle class families of our society cannot afford the load of their charges. Our mission studied their theme properly and decided to provide better higher technical education in computer for every sector of society in affordable charges all over India.<br />
